sections.heading: of wife contracted before marriage; husband not liable
sections.text: The property of the husband shall not be liable for any debts contracted by the wife before marriage.SourceLaws 1877, § 1, p. 33;R.S.1913, § 1565;C.S.1922, § 1514;C.S.1929, § 42-206;R.S.1943, § 42-206.AnnotationsHusband, separated from wife and
